description:
An extension which adds a Windows-like snap assist to GNOME. It changes GNOME's 2 column tiling design to a 2x2 grid. There are also ways to use more complex layouts. Check the README on Github on how to use them and report issues there as well. 

You should remove GNOME's tiling keybindings and set them in the settings of this extension.
name: Tiling assistant
